   },
   "html": "\n[ おがた・たけとら ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n内閣官房長官、内閣書記官長、自由党総裁、情報局総裁、朝日新聞社副社長"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"01a.html\">一覧　（ア）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E7%25B7%2592%25E6%2596%25B9%2520%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E8%2599%258E\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　山形県出身。早稲田大学専門部政経科卒業後、朝日新聞社に入社し、政治部記者。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　欧米留学後、編集局長、主筆、常務取締役、専務取締役、副社長と累進。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　この間、重要産業統制委員、内閣情報部参与を歴任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../p/kfumimar.html\">近衛文麿</a>の新体制運動に呼応し新体制準備委員。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　朝日新聞退社後、<a href=\"../1944/koiso_1.html\">小磯内閣</a>の国務大臣兼情報局総裁に就任。<a href=\"../1945/suzua_1.html\">鈴木（貫）内閣</a>の内閣顧問。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1945/higa_1.html\">東久邇宮内閣</a>では国務大臣、内閣書記官長、情報局総裁を兼任して敗戦処理にあたる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　その後、公職追放に遭い、解除後、自由党から衆院選に初当選。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　吉田内閣④・⑤の副総理・官房長官。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　吉田退陣後、自由党総裁に就任。保守合同に党を率いて参加。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
